[6.6](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/process-engine-6-6)

[6.7](https://docs.doxee.com/docs/en/process-engine-6-7)

**File:** group.ipd

**Shows:** Groups, exception handling, Exception Activity, Exception Connection

**Components:** Start Element, Group, End Element, Exception Activity, Mapping Element, Connection, Exception Connection

This process enters a Group which contains an Exception Activity. Due to the exception thrown by the activity, the group is not completed normally, but left via the Exception Connection instead. It leads to a Mapping Element which transforms the exception variable into an XML, writes it to a variable "error" and logs the message. The End Element provides the error XML in text form as output of the process.
